<body>
	<h3><i>I remove all behaviours from a specified agent or set of agents. </i></h3>
	<h3><font size="2" color="gray">Begin micro-behaviour</font>
	</h3>
	<p><b>REMOVE-ALL-BEHAVIOURS-FROM</b></p>

	<font size="2" color="gray">Begin NetLogo code:</font>
	<pre>substitute-text-area-for target self                                                        
remove-all-behaviours-from target</pre>

	<font size="2" color="gray">End NetLogo code</font>
	<h2>Variants</h2>

	<p>You can add change the agent or agents whose behaviours are removed.</p>

